by ogizanagi at 2015-04-21T22:50:25Z

@javiereguiluz : Sure. I tried your changes on one of my backends, ~~and I still see the drop shadow~~. However, I'm unable to scroll, due to:

```diff
#bootstrap.min.css
@media (min-width: 768px)
.navbar-collapse.collapse {
  display: block!important;
-  height: auto!important;
  padding-bottom: 0;
-  overflow: visible!important;
  visibility: visible!important;
}
```
and
```diff
#admin.css
@media (min-width: 1200px)
#header #header-nav {
  flex: 1;
  height: 0;
  margin: 0;
-  overflow: hidden;
  padding: 0 0 1em;
  width: 222px;
}
```

For me, the problem is solved by replacing the following [css block] (https://github.com/javiereguiluz/EasyAdminBundle/blob/use_bootstrap_header/Resources/views/css/admin.css.twig#L1066) by:
```css
#header #header-nav {
    flex: 1;
    height: 0!important;
    margin: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    overflow-y: auto!important;
    padding: 0 0 1em;
    width: 222px;
}
```

=====
(Or see https://github.com/ogizanagi/EasyAdminBundle/commit/a1739605b33a57191261e956341b95a0d6930eaf)

