by ogizanagi at 2015-04-21T23:01:39Z

NVM, I do not see the drop shadow either without those changes (I had some cache).
I think this is related to the `bootstrap.min.css` setting height to `auto`. The `admin.js` is unable to guess the proper height nor scrolling (basically because there is no scrolling) and cannot add the `drop-shadow` class.

Anyway, the above changes should do the trick :smile:

